Package org.apache.wiki.util.comparators

Class Summary
CollatorComparator A comparator that sorts Strings using a Collator.
HumanComparator A comparator that sorts Strings using "human" ordering, including decimal ordering.
JavaNaturalComparator A comparator that sorts Strings using Java's "natural" order.
LocaleComparator A comparator that sorts Strings using the locale's collator.
PageTimeComparator Compares the lastModified date of its arguments.
